## ğŸ”§ Common Tasks

### Add a New Color
1. Open `/assets/tailwind-config.js`
2. Add to `colors` object in `window.BAMACO_TAILWIND_CONFIG.theme.extend.colors`
3. Use immediately in all HTML files

### Change Hover Effect
1. Open `/assets/tailwind-config.js`
2. Find hover effect classes (after line 110)
3. Modify CSS (transform, box-shadow, border-color)
4. Change applies to ALL pages instantly

### Add New Player/Guild/Article Card
- Use functions in `/assets/script.js`:
  - `createPlayerCard()`
  - `createGuildCard()`
  - `createArticleCard()`
- These use unified hover classes automatically

### Update Page Structure
1. Edit HTML file
2. Use centralized classes from tailwind-config.js
3. Reference assets with correct relative paths
4. Test with navbar.js (centralizes navigation)

